1375
00:55:41,130 --> 00:55:42,530
It's really big.

1376
00:55:43,130 --> 00:55:44,270
It's nice here.

1377
00:55:44,800 --> 00:55:45,900
It's very spacious.

1378
00:55:49,100 --> 00:55:50,370
It's really spacious.

1379
