- Right.

1418
00:57:13,420 --> 00:57:15,660
You didn't understand me, did you?

1419
00:57:16,260 --> 00:57:17,420
(Nodding)

1420
00:57:18,590 --> 00:57:19,630
Don't say "right."

1421
00:57:20,800 --> 00:57:22,229
Don't agree with whatever he says.

1422
00:57:22,230 --> 00:57:23,230
You didn't even understand me.

1423
00:57:23,231 --> 00:57:24,330
I'm sorry, but I'm very tired.

1424
00:57:25,100 --> 00:57:26,730
Just tell me the conclusion.

1425
00:57:27,500 --> 00:57:29,300
There's no conclusion yet. We're still talking.

1426
00:57:29,370 --> 00:57:32,310
Let's say that you win with the stopwatch.

1427
00:57:32,440 --> 00:57:34,709
You either get to decide your room...

1428
00:57:34,710 --> 00:57:36,079
or taking a shower first.

1429
00:57:36,080 --> 00:57:37,650
- It's up to the winner.
- It's up to you.

1430
00:57:38,450 --> 00:57:40,920
You get to decide the item.

1431
00:57:42,320 --> 00:57:43,879
(The stopwatch game is in full swing.)

1432
00:57:43,880 --> 00:57:45,020
Let's play one round like this...

1433
00:57:45,790 --> 00:57:47,560
