1436
00:57:52,460 --> 00:57:53,789
I'm so exhausted.

1437
00:57:53,790 --> 00:57:54,959
(He's already tired before the start.)

1438
00:57:54,960 --> 00:57:56,030
Let's play.

1439
00:57:56,930 --> 00:57:58,369
Ready-or-not, rock-paper-scissors.

1440
00:57:58,370 --> 00:57:59,430
