1444
00:58:11,850 --> 00:58:13,210
- Gosh.
- It's not bad.

1445
00:58:13,850 --> 00:58:16,619
(Kyung Soo, 6)

1446
00:58:16,620 --> 00:58:17,620
(Kyung Soo, 36)

1447
