1520
01:01:07,550 --> 01:01:08,660
Let's vote again.

1521
01:01:08,990 --> 01:01:10,820
Who thinks that Kyung Soo got zero?

1522
01:01:11,660 --> 01:01:12,729
Who doesn't think so?

1523
01:01:12,730 --> 01:01:14,189
This is favorable to Kwang Soo.

1524
01:01:14,190 --> 01:01:15,259
Doh Kyung Soo is out.

1525
01:01:15,260 --> 01:01:16,629
- It's favorable to him.
- It's a majority vote.

1526
01:01:16,630 --> 01:01:18,569
It's favorable to me because I also got zero.

1527
01:01:18,570 --> 01:01:20,400
It's unfavorable to you but not us.

1528
01:01:21,070 --> 01:01:23,839
(The ruling is that both of them got 0.)

1529
01:01:23,840 --> 01:01:25,409
(Kwang Soo, 8)

1530
01:01:25,410 --> 01:01:26,470
Six times eight is forty-eight.

1531
01:01:27,040 --> 01:01:28,040
I won.

1532
01:01:28,180 --> 01:01:29,639
(He gets 1st place amid the confusion.)

1533
01:01:29,640 --> 01:01:30,979
Ready-or-not.

1534
01:01:30,980 --> 01:01:31,980
(Another match to avoid the last place)

1535
01:01:31,981 --> 01:01:34,079
(Woo Bin)

1536
01:01:34,080 --> 01:01:35,150
(Woo Bin, 1)

1537
01:01:35,580 --> 01:01:38,249
(He narrowly avoided 0.)

1538
01:01:38,250 --> 01:01:39,589
(Woo Bin, 1)

1539
01:01:39,590 --> 01:01:40,590
(Woo Bin, 5)

1540
01:01:40,590 --> 01:01:41,590
This isn't so bad.

1541
01:01:42,260 --> 01:01:43,820
What are you talking about?

1542
01:01:46,160 --> 01:01:47,590
