1564
01:02:34,040 --> 01:02:35,539
That's torture.

1565
01:02:35,540 --> 01:02:37,509
- Exactly.
- That's torture.

1566
01:02:37,510 --> 01:02:38,579
(The lower your standing the earlier you must get up.)

1567
01:02:38,580 --> 01:02:39,710
I said this earlier.

1568
01:02:39,850 --> 01:02:41,879
If I'm the first one...

1569
