1581
01:03:05,310 --> 01:03:06,739
(Kwang Soo, 15 Kyung Soo, 6)

1582
01:03:06,740 --> 01:03:09,339
(Kwang Soo, 15 Kyung Soo, 36)

1583
01:03:09,340 --> 01:03:11,710
(He avoided placing last.)

1584
01:03:12,280 --> 01:03:14,880
